headline: 2 Reasons to Watch ZTS and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Over the past six months, Zoetis’s shares (currently trading at $156.80) have posted a disappointing 7% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 8.6% gain. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
